Class PinkBrick

java.lang.Object
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Brick.Brick
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Brick.PinkBrick.PinkBrick
public class PinkBrick extends Brick
The PinkBrick class inherits from Brick, so it has access to all the same methods as Brick. However, it has its own makeBrick method which allows it to have a unique description.

  • Constructor Details

    • PinkBrick

      public PinkBrick(javafx.geometry.Point2D point, javafx.geometry.Dimension2D size)
      Constructs a normal pink brick whose upper-left corner is specified by the Point2D argument. The width and height are specified by the Dimension2D argument.
      Parameters:
      point - a Point2D that is the upper-left corner of the Brick
      size - a Dimension2D, representing width and height of the Brick.
